snippet.title: Skyless Blind - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Skyless Blind is an upcoming surreal space exploration RPGmaker game about uncovering the mysteries of a broken universe. Travel across beautifully ancient worlds and meet strange new friends, collect mystifying artifacts that bend reality, and discover the dark secrets that shattered the skies.

Follow on Twitter
https://twitter.com/SkylessBlind

Join the Discord sever
https://discord.gg/aeCneQVARR

Music by Forgotten Dawn 
https://www.youtube.com/@ForgottenDawn
